rch/pull/3970.diff", "patch_url": "https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/pull/3970.patch"}, "body_html": "<p>This removes volatile from Variable. The functionality is mostly<br>\nreplaced by a global (thread-local) flag, which is controlled by<br>\ntorch.set_grad_enabled() and the context manager torch.no_grad().</p>\n<p>In C++, the flag is exposed through <code>GradMode::is_enabled()</code> and <code>GradMode::set_enabled()</code></p>\n<p><span class=\"issue-keyword tooltipped tooltipped-se\" aria-label=\"This pull request closes issue #3627.\">Fixes</span> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load issue title\" data-id=\"272996917\" data-permission-text=\"Issue title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/3627\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/pytorch/pytorch/issues/3627/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/pytorch/pytorch/issues/3627\">#3627</a></p>", "body_text": "This removes volatile from Variable. The functionality is mostly\nreplaced by a global (thread-local) flag, which is controlled by\ntorch.set_grad_enabled() and the context manager torch.no_grad().\nIn C++, the flag is exposed through GradMode::is_enabled() and GradMode::set_enabled()\nFixes #3627", "body": "This removes volatile from Variable. The functionality is mostly\r\nreplaced by a global (thread-local) flag, which is controlled by\r\ntorch.set_grad_enabled() and the context manager torch.no_grad().\r\n\r\nIn C++, the flag is exposed through `GradMode::is_enabled()` and `GradMode::set_enabled()`\r\n\r\nFixes #3627"}